lastCommitMessage: Refactor ProductPurchaseConfirmPage for improved shipping options and error handling
- Introduced a ShippingService to manage shipping options and address synchronization, enhancing modularity.
- Implemented caching for subtotal and currency calculations to optimize performance.
- Enhanced error handling during shipping option initialization, providing user feedback for failures.
- Refactored UI components for better organization and readability, including dedicated methods for building sections of the purchase confirmation page.
- Improved state management for shipping options and addresses, ensuring a smoother user experience during checkout.
